show.title: War God's Order
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/vwWXE6
show.description: Steven, once dismissed by everyone as a failure, returns after five years with a mysterious Golden Card, determined to avenge his family's death. Unknown to even his wife Rozy, Steven hides a secret identity—he is the true master of the Golden Card, a cunning strategist capable of manipulating the entire world at his will. As he brings the city's mafia to their knees one by one, a wall stands between him and his love: their own family. But why are they against him? How will Steven reclaim his lost happiness? And will Rozy ever uncover the truth about the man she thought she knew?
